data.description: This charming Northside home features four bedrooms and two baths, offering comfortable living for families and individuals alike. The property features a fenced yard for privacy and security, along with an additional detached garage, perfect for extra storage or a workshop. Inside, you'll find modern updates, including newer laminate flooring and plush carpeting for a cozy feel. The kitchen showcases a stunning backsplash, adding a touch of elegance to meal prep. The spacious lower level hosts a large family room, ideal for entertainment and relaxation. This home combines practicality with style, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a warm and inviting living space on the Northside.
